             sworn. - Where did you get that watch from? - 
               <persName id="t18050220-13-person179">A. John North</persName>
             came on the 3d of February, about half-past three o'clock, and left that watch.</p>
               <p>Q. The same watch that you gave to Smith? - A. Yes. (The watch identified by the Prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I was going to call 
               <persName id="t18050220-13-person180">
                  James 
                  Clay
               <interp inst="t18050220-13-person180" type="surname" value="Clay"></interp>
